    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 6th level, as a bonus action the ki you control can be used to grant you a flying speed of to your walking speed that lasts for 10 minutes. However while flying in this way, the attack range of your Sun Soul Bolt is reduced to 60 feet.</p><p>You can use this feature a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus, and you regain all expended uses when you finish a long rest.</p><p>Additionally, when you use your Patient Defense, any creature that misses you with an attack must make a Constitution saving throw. On a failure they are blinded until the end your next turn.</p><p>Starting at 13th level, the damage types you can reduce and damage you deal with your Deflect Harm includes all damage types but psychic.</p>",
